{"type": "article", "id": 5040, "title": "方便控水的漏斗锅", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-08T08:04:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233632jzWgkewJcfEp2And.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款来自韩国设计师 Bosoon Kang 的创意产品，Funnel Pot 是一款便于用户控水的锅具，整个造型与我们常见的长手柄锅具并无太大差别，但 Bosoon Kang 却把把手的位置做成了空心状，并设计了一个可拆卸的滤网在里面，这样就可以方便用户轻松地将锅内多余地水或者汁液倒出，还能够避免食材随着水流出，让滤水倒水这种小步骤变得更加高效。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233631MNAvs3WjGpaSEgXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233631CU8LqsY3OkyV0HlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233632C3jbAZxoJQLfF8Gy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}